commander
Class CommandManager

java.lang.Object
  commander.CommandManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.Observer
public class CommandManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer

This class is responsible for holding system commands, whether self-invoked or indirectly-invoked by the user (through UI).

Author:
Or Shwartz, Itay Evron
